Cell["\<\
Plot the mutual information averaged over the quantum trajectories. Here, \
\[Gamma] refers to the damping rate, which equals to 1 in our unit system:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->653137184,ExpressionUUID->"22f1dab7-cd6e-4d75-b309-2107af035bda"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"ListLinePlot", "[", 
